Alas!
The church should have no political alignment.
The approaching Allied forces.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>snippets</title><link>https://zkazure.github.io/posts/learn-snippets/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zkazure.github.io/posts/learn-snippets/</guid><description>&lt;p>In the doom emacs the defaut directory is &lt;code>~/.doom.d/snippets/&lt;/code> . And in the the file should be divided into different derctory to triger different file in the corresponding mode.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="front-matter">front-matter&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">#&lt;/span> -*- mode: snippet -*-
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">#&lt;/span> name: the name to search
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">#&lt;/span> key: the key word to be completed by &amp;lt;tab&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">#&lt;/span> condition: if here is &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">nil&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">,&lt;/span> the snippet will not be trigger
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">#&lt;/span> --
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="variables">variables&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="main">main&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>${1:default_value}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>${2:label}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>${2:same}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 插入 snippets 后可以使用 &amp;lt;tab&amp;gt; 按顺序跳转。&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 里面的默认值可以用作提示&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 还可以插入相同的值&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>${0}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 这个是最后的光标位置&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>${cursor}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 使用后会自动跳转，也就意味着不能够修改其他的${数字}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="advance">advance&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-emacs-lisp" data-lang="emacs-lisp">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>${CILPBOARD}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 从当前的剪切版中获取信息&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>${SECLRCTION}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 从当前选择的内容中获取信息&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 但是似乎难以决定输入的位置&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">;; 不如使用 ${CILPBOARD}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="other">Other&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>$date&lt;/code>: 日期&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>$time&lt;/code>: 时间&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>$file&lt;/code>: filename&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>$filepath&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>`(format-time-string &amp;quot;%Y-%m-%d&amp;quot;)`&lt;/code>: 用于设定时间&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>可以利用``来调用 elisp&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>summary</title><link>https://zkazure.github.io/posts/org-summary/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://zkazure.github.io/posts/org-summary/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>please ignore the &amp;lsquo;,&amp;rsquo; at the beggining.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-org" data-lang="org">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">#+TITLE&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">: No matter uppercase or not&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">#+AUTHOR&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">: me&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="heading">Heading&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-org" data-lang="org">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>*&lt;span style="font-weight:bold"> the first heading&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">**&lt;/span> second
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">***&lt;/span> third
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">**&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"> TODO&lt;/span> every heading can be a TODO
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="annotation">Annotation&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>bold&lt;/strong> &lt;em>italic&lt;/em> &lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->underline&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --> &lt;del>delete&lt;/del> &lt;code>code&lt;/code> &lt;code>code&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="list">List&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-org" data-lang="org">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>itemize
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">- &lt;/span>item1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">+ &lt;/span>item2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>item&lt;/li>
&lt;li>item&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-org" data-lang="org">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>enumerate
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">1.&lt;/span> item-1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">2)&lt;/span> item-2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>A. item-A
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>B) item-B
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>first&lt;/li>
&lt;li>second&lt;/li>
&lt;li>aa&lt;/li>
&lt;li>bb&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted -->
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-org" data-lang="org">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">- [ ]&lt;/span> not started
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">- &lt;/span>[-] in process
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">- [X]&lt;/span> finished
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;input disabled="" type="checkbox"> not started&lt;/li>
&lt;li>[-] in process&lt;/li>
